{"tid":366073,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[只屌一次系列] hoko farm","createTime":"2017-08-19T17:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T05:37:49.000Z","uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5015903352d3d60deec6742e9b7f146ed70adc82","tid":366073,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T17:21:53.000Z","msg":"上網見到啲相好似好好食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就去馬<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/011354_35b9b9efdac2a6817ec52f7bbf438f15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F011354_35b9b9efdac2a6817ec52f7bbf438f15.jpg&h=a61b5dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到無乜人。。ok唔驚嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一黎就比個綠茶包你，幾好食熱辣辣但好細個<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/011425_0e193c250475bc9c758a878192d4cc35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F011425_0e193c250475bc9c758a878192d4cc35.jpg&h=3e3005ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加錢轉餐有個甘荀湯，唔錯，夠熱幾甜<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/011505_7b3b420d7366094e777bf2139e0593df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F011505_7b3b420d7366094e777bf2139e0593df.jpg&h=72f6b961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n芝士焗魚柳螺絲粉<br />\n個魚係岩岩炸起，係幾正嘅，成盤都係熱辣辣岩岩焗起咁<br />\n但<br />\n個汁點解<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有好立克味？</span><br />\nWhy why tell me why..<br />\n我食左兩啖頂唔順<br />\n想像下好立克焗螺絲粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/011549_52d6e25e82fe0d5f23f77e844764dcf5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F011549_52d6e25e82fe0d5f23f77e844764dcf5.jpg&h=cf43cef7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係西冷，un到要即刻book睇牙<br />\n個汁就普通燒烤汁，薯角岩岩焗起係正嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/011813_38da823572baa338d0f75aeb86407015.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F011813_38da823572baa338d0f75aeb86407015.jpg&h=018e1116&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/011814_38da823572baa338d0f75aeb86407015.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F011814_38da823572baa338d0f75aeb86407015.jpg&h=f47be8b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有兩杯淡過水嘅凍朱古力就算吧啦。。飲到心都淡埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n埋單二百六<br />\n我心目中呢餐只值五十六。<br />\n<br />\n還我美好星期六<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4512af2865fa736fcfa4c2edffe45a8e8f1034","tid":366073,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe38e10d2a96b00f518ce3ad611fd32408e85bc","tid":366073,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ca88f31f16afff0a26d2c6876f080a97a295e4","tid":366073,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:40:36.000Z","msg":"係咪北海道熊牧場啲fd"},{"pid":"3d2690411164f7b0a166f7ac9cc3136b8216370e","tid":366073,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:02:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪北海道熊牧場啲fd</blockquote><br />\n有啲似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但邊個難食啲好難講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0118741482572d8254c9b10d023f8ae3a74570f","tid":366073,"uid":49130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:37:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪北海道熊牧場啲fd</blockquote><br />\n有啲似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但邊個難食啲好難講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n北海道牧場好垃圾<br />\nd 人連飲品都唔識沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}